Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Rancher Card & Adventure Video Games: Monster Rancher Explorer Archive (Game Boy Color): Strategy: Level 51
By Y.K. TAN on Sunday, May 30, 2004 - 10:36 pm:

Stage 51

Uh, at the start, just destroy all the boxes beneath you to obtain a nifty sum of fireworks. After that you have destroy all boxes, recreate just one specific box just beneath the first jell reproducer. Once a jell land on it, destroy the box killing the jell. After that remake that same box in the same place and jump right up to the second level (before you do that, remove those three extra boxes on the second level.)

After that is achieve, remove boxes to form gaps so that the second jell won't attack you from now on. At the most leftern part of screen, create gaps so that the naga will fall through nicely when it moves to the left. After that, box nicely upwards and once a naga fell again, make your way to the golden key, and come back, destroying a box so as to prevent the naga from reaching you.

Remove the box in which the 2nd naga will fall on, so that after that, you would gain access to the higher level and reach the door.
